<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="those-pron">those <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðəʊz/    美 /ðoʊz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>那些；那些人；那些物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Those are my books.
那些是我的书。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Only those who will risk going too far can possibly find out how far one can go.  
只有那些愿意冒险不断前行的人，才能知道自己能够走多远。</p><footer>——艾略特</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Half of <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ surveyed in 16 countries say they go first to their closest friend to share their deepest wishes and darkest fears.   （2013 浙江改）  </li>
<li>At our factory there are a few machines similar to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ described in this magazine.  （2013 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. those  2. those  </p></div>